# Modern Dark Theme Style Guide

This style guide establishes a sophisticated, professional dark theme design system that balances enterprise functionality with modern consumer polish. The aesthetic emphasizes clarity, data visualization, and premium user experience through carefully orchestrated contrast and refined typography.

## Color Palette

### Primary Colors
- **Primary Black** - #000000 (Main background, creating depth and sophistication)
- **Primary White** - #FFFFFF (Primary text and high-contrast elements)
- **Surface Dark** - #1A1A1A (Card backgrounds and elevated surfaces)

### Secondary Colors
- **Secondary Gray Dark** - #2D2D2D (Secondary surfaces and subtle backgrounds)
- **Secondary Gray Medium** - #4A4A4A (Borders and dividers)
- **Secondary Gray Light** - #9CA3AF (Secondary text and disabled states)

### Accent Colors
- **Accent Blue** - #3B82F6 (Primary actions, links, and data visualization)
- **Accent Green** - #10B981 (Success states and positive metrics)
- **Accent Orange** - #F59E0B (Warnings and highlights)
- **Accent Red** - #EF4444 (Errors and critical actions)

### Functional Colors
- **Success Green** - #059669 (Confirmation messages and success indicators)
- **Error Red** - #DC2626 (Error states and destructive actions)
- **Warning Orange** - #D97706 (Warning states and caution indicators)
- **Info Blue** - #2563EB (Information and neutral notifications)

### Background Variants
- **Background Primary** - #000000 (Main application background)
- **Background Secondary** - #0F0F0F (Subtle variation for sections)
- **Background Card** - #1F1F1F (Card and modal backgrounds)
- **Background Hover** - #2A2A2A (Interactive element hover states)

## Typography

### Font Family
- **Primary Font**: Inter (Web primary)
- **Secondary Font**: SF Pro Display (macOS)
- **Fallback Font**: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto

### Font Weights
- **Light**: 300
- **Regular**: 400
- **Medium**: 500
- **Semibold**: 600
- **Bold**: 700
- **Heavy**: 800

### Text Styles

#### Headings
- **H1**: 48px/56px, Bold, Letter spacing -0.5px
  - Used for hero sections and primary page titles
- **H2**: 36px/44px, Bold, Letter spacing -0.3px
  - Used for major section headers and feature titles
- **H3**: 28px/36px, Semibold, Letter spacing -0.2px
  - Used for subsection headers and component titles
- **H4**: 24px/32px, Semibold, Letter spacing -0.1px
  - Used for card headers and secondary titles

#### Body Text
- **Body Large**: 18px/28px, Regular, Letter spacing 0px
  - Primary reading text for main content areas
- **Body**: 16px/24px, Regular, Letter spacing 0px
  - Standard text for most UI elements and descriptions
- **Body Small**: 14px/20px, Regular, Letter spacing 0.1px
  - Secondary information and supporting text

#### Specialized Text
- **Caption**: 12px/16px, Medium, Letter spacing 0.5px
  - Labels, timestamps, and metadata
- **Button Large**: 16px/24px, Semibold, Letter spacing 0.2px
  - Primary and secondary button text
- **Button Small**: 14px/20px, Medium, Letter spacing 0.3px
  - Compact buttons and inline actions
- **Link Text**: 16px/24px, Medium, Letter spacing 0px, Accent Blue
  - Clickable text elements throughout the application

## Component Styling

### Primary Button
- **Background**: Accent Blue (#3B82F6)
- **Text**: Primary White (#FFFFFF)
- **Height**: 48px
- **Corner Radius**: 8px
- **Padding**: 24px horizontal, 12px vertical
- **Hover State**: Background darkens to #2563EB
- **Active State**: Background darkens to #1D4ED8

### Secondary Button
- **Border**: 2px Accent Blue (#3B82F6)
- **Text**: Accent Blue (#3B82F6)
- **Background**: Transparent
- **Height**: 48px
- **Corner Radius**: 8px
- **Padding**: 22px horizontal, 10px vertical
- **Hover State**: Background fills with Accent Blue, text becomes white

### Ghost Button
- **Text**: Primary White (#FFFFFF)
- **Background**: Transparent
- **Height**: 44px
- **Hover State**: Background becomes Background Hover (#2A2A2A)

### Card Component
- **Background**: Background Card (#1F1F1F)
- **Border**: 1px Secondary Gray Medium (#4A4A4A)
- **Corner Radius**: 12px
- **Padding**: 24px
- **Shadow**: None (relies on border for definition)

### Input Fields
- **Height**: 48px
- **Corner Radius**: 8px
- **Border**: 1px Secondary Gray Medium (#4A4A4A)
- **Active Border**: 2px Accent Blue (#3B82F6)
- **Background**: Background Card (#1F1F1F)
- **Text**: Primary White (#FFFFFF)
- **Placeholder Text**: Secondary Gray Light (#9CA3AF)
- **Padding**: 16px horizontal

### Navigation Elements
- **Background**: Background Card (#1F1F1F)
- **Active Item**: Background Hover (#2A2A2A) with Accent Blue indicator
- **Text**: Primary White (#FFFFFF)
- **Secondary Text**: Secondary Gray Light (#9CA3AF)
- **Dividers**: Secondary Gray Medium (#4A4A4A)

### Icons
- **Primary Icons**: 24px x 24px
- **Small Icons**: 20px x 20px
- **Large Icons**: 32px x 32px
- **Interactive Color**: Accent Blue (#3B82F6)
- **Secondary Color**: Secondary Gray Light (#9CA3AF)
- **Style**: Outlined with 2px stroke weight

## Spacing System

- **4px** - Micro spacing (tight element relationships)
- **8px** - Small spacing (internal component padding)
- **12px** - Compact spacing (related elements)
- **16px** - Default spacing (standard margins and padding)
- **24px** - Medium spacing (component separation)
- **32px** - Large spacing (section separation)
- **48px** - Extra large spacing (major layout divisions)
- **64px** - XXL spacing (page-level separations)

## Motion & Animation

### Transition Timing
- **Micro Interactions**: 150ms, ease-out
- **Standard Transitions**: 250ms, ease-in-out
- **Complex Animations**: 400ms, cubic-bezier(0.4, 0.0, 0.2, 1)
- **Page Transitions**: 350ms, cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94)

### Animation Principles
- **Subtle Entrance**: Elements fade in with slight upward movement
- **Hover Effects**: Scale (1.02) with shadow enhancement
- **Data Visualization**: Smooth chart animations with staggered reveals
- **Loading States**: Skeleton screens with subtle shimmer effects

## Data Visualization

### Chart Colors
- **Primary Series**: Accent Blue (#3B82F6)
- **Secondary Series**: Accent Green (#10B981)
- **Tertiary Series**: Accent Orange (#F59E0B)
- **Additional Series**: Sequential blue variations from light to dark

### Grid and Axes
- **Grid Lines**: Secondary Gray Medium (#4A4A4A) at 0.3 opacity
- **Axis Labels**: Secondary Gray Light (#9CA3AF)
- **Axis Lines**: Secondary Gray Medium (#4A4A4A)

## Accessibility Considerations

### Contrast Ratios
- **Primary Text on Dark Background**: 21:1 (exceeds WCAG AAA)
- **Secondary Text on Dark Background**: 7:1 (exceeds WCAG AA)
- **Interactive Elements**: Minimum 4.5:1 contrast ratio
- **Focus Indicators**: 2px Accent Blue outline with 2px offset

### Interactive States
- **Focus**: 2px Accent Blue outline
- **Hover**: Background color change with smooth transition
- **Active**: Slight scale reduction (0.98) with color change
- **Disabled**: 0.5 opacity with cursor not-allowed